Package: listchr
Type: Package
Title: List Columns to Character Conversion
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(
	  "Pierre-Yves", "Berrard",
	  email = "pierre.yves.berrard@gmail.com",
	  role = c("aut", "cre")
	)
Description:
    Flattens list-columns of a data frame into strings,
    in order to export under a more simple format (csv, ...).
    The reverse transformation (separated string to list) can
    also be done. 
Depends: R (>= 3.3)
Imports: dplyr (>= 0.7)
Suggests: testthat
URL: http://github.com/the-knife/listchr
BugReports: http://github.com/the-knife/listchr/issues
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
